    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of usable life for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option for commuting, light duty, or a project, and it represents strong value for anyone seeking dependable basics without a big price tag. An honest opportunity to get behind the wheel at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
