      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this car would make a great project, parts car, or simple around-town runabout for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle being offered at a price that leaves plenty of room to make it your own. If you like finding value and don\u2019t mind a bit of TLC, this could be a fun and practical pickup.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid candidate for someone who wants an affordable driver/project with real upside. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers a dependable powertrain foundation, responsive throttle input, and the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes ownership approachable. Starts, runs, and moves, with the sort of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a budget entry point rather than hidden pretenses. Great fit for a hands-on buyer looking for inexpensive transportation, a weekend fixer, or a platform to sort and improve over time. If you know how to spot value in a rough-around-the-edges car, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Used and rough, priced to sell fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still turns heads for all the right reasons: full of personality, unmistakable presence, and ready for someone with vision to give it its next chapter. It has the honest, well-lived character that makes a used car feel like more than transportation\u2014it feels like a project, a daily driver with attitude, or the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates potential over perfection. If you\u2019re looking for an affordable entry point into something with real charm and plenty of story left to write, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Well-suited for a budget-conscious buyer, this vehicle offers straightforward value with plenty of usable life for the right owner. It presents as an affordable opportunity for local driving, a backup car, or a practical project, and it\u2019s priced to reflect strong value in today\u2019s market. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive transportation from a seller you can buy from with confidence, this is a compelling option.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a project with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could be a great fit for someone handy or anyone after affordable wheels without spending a fortune. A sensible buy for the right person, with lots of potential at a very approachable price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
