      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Ready for a hands-on owner, this car is a solid project with the kind of honest character enthusiasts look for. The drivetrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels fundamentally usable, and it presents as a worthwhile platform for restoration, weekend wrenching, or budget fun. Cosmetic and age-related needs are present, but the car retains good bones and a mechanically straightforward layout that makes it especially appealing for someone who appreciates classic, analog motoring. Priced to move for a buyer who sees the potential.",
